metadata.name: Ethereal
metadata.description:
When the righteous come forth to witness a new dawn , put aside our woes and sing a new song
They put aside the old man and it feels less of itself , a man outgrowing his present knowledge of self
I was the old man, I tasted water in the ocean , I found a new peace and I owned it.
I believed every wave that I felt I knew it was my time, My time of purity, my time of rejuvenation. 
The realm of been a spirit being was a new phase for me but still it was my time and i will explore these etherealms as they guide me to a higher self. - Dweirdo
